  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      the purpose of this study is to show that the vacuum control surgical bleeding helps stop
      bleeding extraMD (MD: Medical Device) at the orifice of the retrograde cannulation during a
      heart with Extra-corporeal circulation (ECC),
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
